				</p>
				<p class="footer-company-name">Dojo Dev Technologies Â© 2023</p>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-center">
				<div>
				<i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i>
				<p><span>123 Baywalk Boulevard</span> Manila, PH</p>
				</div>
				<div>
				<i class="fa fa-phone"></i>
				<p>+63.555.555.5555</p>
